/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a serene moment on a street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a car on the road, giving a driver's view of the surroundings. The sky above is a clear blue, with the sun shining brightly, casting a warm glow over the scene. On either side of the road, lush green trees stand tall, their leaves rustling in the breeze. Buildings peek through the foliage, adding a touch of urbanity to the otherwise natural landscape. Power lines crisscross above, forming a network against the sky. The image is taken from a low angle, making the viewer feel as if they are part of the scene, ready to drive down the road and explore what lies ahead.
